notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-15T19:41:35.150Z",maintainer-agent,"Companion-repo SDK doc duplication evidence (pass #90, 2026-07-15): unbraind/pm-cli-companion hosts docs/TYPESCRIPT_SDK.md — a full parallel \"TypeScript SDK Guide ... covers every capability type with working examples\" — alongside website-server/views/sdk.ejs, while the canonical in-repo doc is docs/SDK.md (2265 lines). Two hand-maintained full SDK guides in two repos = drift by construction; fold into this item's \"website/plugin copy still to check\" ledger. Fix direction at execution: generate the companion page from the canonical doc (or reduce it to a pointer + quickstart), never hand-sync. In-repo SDK docs trio (SDK.md / SDK_CUSTOMIZATION_PRIMITIVES.md / SDK_PRIMITIVE_INVENTORY.md) verified deliberately partitioned with distinct purposes and tracked owners — no in-repo duplication defect."
